    "Subject": "Confirma tu suscripción a Buba Beauty Studio",
    "Html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"es\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n<meta name=\"x-apple-disable-message-reformatting\">\n<title>Confirma tu suscripción a Buba Beauty Studio</title>\n<link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@400;500;600&family=DM+Sans:wght@400;500;700&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n<!--[if mso]>\n<style type=\"text/css\">\n  body, table, td, a, p, h1 { font-family: Georgia, serif !important; }\n</style>\n<![endif]-->\n</head>\n<body style=\"margin:0; padding:0; background-color:#FAF7F4; font-family:'DM Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color:#2D2D2D;\">\n<center style=\"width:100%; background-color:#FAF7F4;\">\n  <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"background-color:#FAF7F4;\">\n    <tr>\n      <td align=\"center\" style=\"padding:32px 16px;\">\n        <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"600\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"max-width:600px; width:100%; background-color:#FFFFFF; border:1px solid #E8D5C4;\">\n\n          <!-- Logo frame -->\n          <tr>\n            <td align=\"center\" style=\"padding:40px 24px 16px 24px;\">\n              <table role=\"presentation\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\">\n                <tr>\n                  <td align=\"center\" style=\"border:2px solid #C9A87C; padding:20px 32px;\">\n                    <p style=\"margin:0; font-family:'Cormorant Garamond', Georgia, serif; font-size:28px; font-weight:500; letter-spacing:2px; color:#1A1A1A;\">BUBA</p>\n                    <p style=\"margin:4px 0 0 0; font-family:'DM Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size:10px; letter-spacing:3px; color:#C9A87C; text-transform:uppercase;\">Beauty Studio</p>\n                  </td>\n                </tr>\n              </table>\n            </td>\n          </tr>\n\n          <!-- Heading -->\n          <tr>\n            <td align=\"center\" style=\"padding:24px 32px 8px 32px;\">\n              <h1 style=\"margin:0; font-family:'Cormorant Garamond', Georgia, serif; font-size:32px; font-weight:500; color:#1A1A1A; line-height:1.2;\">Confirma tu suscripción</h1>\n            </td>\n          </tr>\n\n          <!-- Body -->\n          <tr>\n            <td style=\"padding:16px 40px 8px 40px;\">\n              <p style=\"margin:0 0 16px 0; font-family:'DM Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size:16px; line-height:1.6; color:#2D2D2D;\">Hola,</p>\n              <p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0; font-family:'DM Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size:16px; line-height:1.6; color:#2D2D2D;\">Gracias por apuntarte a las novedades de Buba Beauty Studio. Confirma tu email haciendo clic en el botón de abajo — así nos aseguramos de que eres tú.</p>\n            </td>\n          </tr>\n\n          <!-- CTA button -->\n          <tr>\n            <td align=\"center\" style=\"padding:16px 32px 32px 32px;\">\n              <table role=\"presentation\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\">\n                <tr>\n                  <td align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#C9A87C\" style=\"background-color:#C9A87C;\">\n                    <a href=\"{{confirm_url}}\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"display:inline-block; padding:16px 40px; font-family:'DM Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size:14px; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:2px; color:#FFFFFF; text-decoration:none; text-transform:uppercase;\">Confirmar suscripción</a>\n                  </td>\n                </tr>\n              </table>\n            </td>\n          </tr>\n\n          <!-- Small print -->\n          <tr>\n            <td style=\"padding:0 40px 40px 40px;\">\n              <p style=\"margin:0; font-family:'DM Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size:13px; line-height:1.6; color:#8A8A8A; text-align:center;\">Este enlace expira en {{confirm_expires_in}}. Si no fuiste tú, ignora este email.</p>\n            </td>\n          </tr>\n\n          <!-- Divider -->\n          <tr>\n            <td style=\"padding:0 40px;\">\n              <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\">\n                <tr><td height=\"1\" style=\"background-color:#E8D5C4; font-size:0; line-height:0;\">&nbsp;</td></tr>\n              </table>\n            </td>\n          </tr>\n\n          <!-- Footer -->\n          <tr>\n            <td align=\"center\" style=\"padding:24px 32px 32px 32px;\">\n              <p style=\"margin:0 0 8px 0; font-family:'Cormorant Garamond', Georgia, serif; font-size:18px; color:#1A1A1A;\">Buba Beauty Studio</p>\n              <p style=\"margin:0 0 4px 0; font-family:'DM Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size:13px; line-height:1.6; color:#2D2D2D;\">Rúa Curtis, 8 · 15009 A Coruña</p>\n              <p style=\"margin:0 0 12px 0; font-family:'DM Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size:13px; line-height:1.6; color:#2D2D2D;\">+34 604 028 359</p>\n              <p style=\"margin:0 0 16px 0; font-family:'DM Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size:13px;\">\n                <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/bubabeautystudio/\" style=\"color:#C9A87C; text-decoration:none;\">Instagram</a>\n              </p>\n              <p style=\"margin:0; font-family:'DM Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size:11px; line-height:1.6; color:#8A8A8A;\">\n                <a href=\"{{amazonSESUnsubscribeUrl}}\" style=\"color:#8A8A8A; text-decoration:underline;\">Cancelar suscripción</a>\n                &nbsp;·&nbsp;\n                <a href=\"{{amazonSESListManagementUrl}}\" style=\"color:#8A8A8A; text-decoration:underline;\">Gestionar preferencias</a>\n              </p>\n            </td>\n          </tr>\n\n        </table>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </table>\n</center>\n</body>\n</html>\n",
    "Text": "BUBA BEAUTY STUDIO\n==================\n\nConfirma tu suscripción\n\nHola,\n\nGracias por apuntarte a las novedades de Buba Beauty Studio. Confirma tu email entrando en el siguiente enlace — así nos aseguramos de que eres tú.\n\nConfirmar suscripción:\n{{confirm_url}}\n\nEste enlace expira en {{confirm_expires_in}}. Si no fuiste tú, ignora este email.\n\n---\n\nBuba Beauty Studio\nRúa Curtis, 8 · 15009 A Coruña\n+34 604 028 359\nInstagram: https://www.instagram.com/bubabeautystudio/\n\nCancelar suscripción: {{amazonSESUnsubscribeUrl}}\nGestionar preferencias: {{amazonSESListManagementUrl}}\n"
  }
}